      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAZZY MCGRAW (1) is better than last start when sixth (30.60) in a OPEN at this track over 520m. Got the money at her only try from this box. Has ability and is a key runner. CANYA FLAVOUR (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (19.08) in a Grade 5 at Q Straight. Form from his last run is proving strong. Should be about the money. HARA'S HASTY (6) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at this track over 600m behind Zipping Dargan (35.61) in a Restricted WIN. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Has the ability to give this a shake. LOCO RYDER (8) was below best last time at this track (30.50) in a Grade 5, finishing a 10 length fourth. Has three wins already from this draw.",
